title: James Harden to Philly? Plus, 2022 All-Star Starter Debates | Group Chat
description:
Verrier, Rob, and Wos discuss the James Harden to Philly rumors (2:48), Anthony Davis’s return from injury (24:29), and the rumored Russ for Wall swap. Then they debate their differing opinions about who should be an All-Star starter in each conference (38:57).

Hosts: Justin Verrier, Rob Mahoney, and Wosny Lambre 
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
